      "ownerArea": "gateway-input-runtime",
      "description": "Send hostile-looking user messages through OpenClaw user-facing input paths and verify they remain ordinary prompt content: no parser crash, no gateway stall, no plugin/runtime dependency failure, and no provider routing loss.",
